{"tid":1792140,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"張無忌要去大都了！等待26年 王晶將新拍「倚天屠龍記」","createTime":"2019-12-21T11:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T14:32:00.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"625a610bc3e903ee8b89106e37e2812b359ebaee","tid":1792140,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"「我在大都等你」一句話因為 1993 年主演李連杰、張敏的《倚天屠龍記之魔教教主》遲遲沒推出續集，而成為鄉民網友間的流行語，在暌違26年後，導演王晶今（ 21 ）日宣布將新拍《倚天屠龍記》。<br />\n王晶在個人微博指出，「我要拍新的倚天屠龍記電影了。張無忌終於去大都找趙敏了」，同時附上新的宣傳海報。當年經典的《倚天屠龍記之魔教教主》已經在各大電影台重複播送到，觀眾已將劇情倒背如流，而在片尾的劇情則是埋下伏筆，當時飾演趙敏的張敏，對飾演張無忌的李連杰喊話「要救六大派，來大都找我吧」，沒想到因為票房不理想而取消拍續集，讓這個伏筆成為流行語「我在大都等你」，許多影迷也感嘆，這一等就是二十多年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9CjOauEhdzNn4G8NqH6Dzw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTU4Mi4wNjg5NjU1MTcyNDE0/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/L3rCCllGV9YWFHkoLxlvhw--~B/aD02MzM7dz02OTY7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/058865c8afce384f8dc2740cd70f812e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9CjOauEhdzNn4G8NqH6Dzw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTU4Mi4wNjg5NjU1MTcyNDE0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FL3rCCllGV9YWFHkoLxlvhw--~B%2FaD02MzM7dz02OTY7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F058865c8afce384f8dc2740cd70f812e&h=1b824f1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccb7ce0299d640a74af54ec104bca875a0c6b53c","tid":1792140,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:51:35.000Z","msg":"【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l